erface mirrors Word’s ribbon layout.","Ability Write, just like Word, has a clean, well-organized design that will be easy for new users to master. Not only is the design functional, it is also easy on the eyes thanks to clever shading and highlighting of the toolbar and buttons.","On the right side of the screen on some versions, the software displays a Recent Files and Folders menu that displays all of your recently used documents so that you can open them quickly. This feature is useful for switching between various files while you work.","Ability Write has the features necessary for basic word processing, and it also has some of the same features as Microsoft Word. There are pre-made templates to expedite document creation, so you can create professional-looking envelopes and labels. You can also change text to preset styles instantly.","There are many basic features that the software lacks, though. You cannot highlight text, for instance, or create watermarks to protect your documents in some versions. This word processing software also lacks many common editing tools. There are no citation and bibliography features for adding important citation information to the end of a document, for example.","Though there is a spellchecker and grammar checker, there is no dictionary look-up feature that allows you find a word&#39;s synonyms, antonyms or definition. Further, it has no tracking or notation features to document changes to a document or to keep track of ideas, so it’s less effective than other applications if you need to collaborate and share documents.","However, it does have the ability to save files in all Microsoft Word formats, as well as PDF, rich text and plain text formats.","Ability Write, the word processing element of Ability Office, is not particularly unique word processing software. It has basic functionality, and includes a few more advanced features – such as some templates. It can’t compare to the robust features of Word, but for casual users it has plenty of features for the most basic word processing jobs."]},"id":"32f9bb7c-e456-4d3a-99ac-2c51fe96cf69","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_49285","url":"/ability-write-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"w5zRTt8zKNM8ERYhxFTX9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-04-16T19:52:12Z","datePublished":"2010-04-16T19:52:12Z","name":"Ability Write","synopsis":"Ability Write is the word processing software available with the Ability Office suite by ASI.","review":{"rating":43,"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Ability Write is the word processing software available with the Ability Office suite by ASI.","language":"en","dateModified":"2010-04-16T19:52:12Z","id":"QoHPZ4xd9sY9wx6EcETFYU","meta":{"title":"Ability Write Review | Top Ten Reviews","description":"Ability Write is great software for casual users, but may not work well if you use word processing software every day. Learn more here."},"products":[{"slug":"ability-write","url":"/product/ability-write","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T22:23:17Z","name":"Ability Write","dateModified":"2019-04-17T22:23:17Z","id":"iYQDdJwjj432nUbUUoRoYN","dateImported":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-17T22:23:17Z","type":"review","template":"review","social":{"twitter":{"image":{"status":"","height":0,"path":"/L89szhPaE4v59KTXNaWEEe.jpg","checksum":"","copyright":"","fileSize":0,"width":0,"caption":"","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T22:23:17Z","mimeType":"","name":"49257-ability-write-5-box.jpg","importSrc":"/i/rev/prod/ce/49257-ability-write-5-box.jpg","credit":"","dateModified":"2019-04-17T22:23:17Z","id":"L89szhPaE4v59KTXNaWEEe","dateImported":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","site":"toptenreviews","orientation":"","mos":"h